1
00:00:00,433 --> 00:00:01,733
I'm getting tired of you.

2
00:00:01,966 --> 00:00:03,300
It's not starting, Chok.

3
00:00:03,866 --> 00:00:06,400
You're tired of me ever since
you've met him.

4
00:00:06,966 --> 00:00:09,199
Be honest with me,
in your heart right now...

5
00:00:09,733 --> 00:00:11,400
have you ever seen good in me?

6
00:00:11,933 --> 00:00:14,766
I did everything for you.
Always let you do anything.

7
00:00:14,966 --> 00:00:18,133
But is this what you repay me for
what I've done for you?

8
00:00:18,133 --> 00:00:19,566
Stop being a whiny bitch.

9
00:00:20,133 --> 00:00:21,133
To be honest,

10
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:23,199
I never was being serious with you.

11
00:00:24,033 --> 00:00:26,033
If I have a choice, I won't choose you.

12
00:00:26,433 --> 00:00:28,833
Chok! You're being mean now.

13
00:00:36,033 --> 00:00:37,333
I do not love you!

14
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,300
Get out of my life now!

15
00:00:45,433 --> 00:00:46,500
Damn it!

16
00:01:24,433 --> 00:01:26,699
Here, I bought you some flowers.

17
00:01:27,666 --> 00:01:30,433
How did you know that I like this flower?

18
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,633
Isn't a boyfriend supposed to know?

19
00:01:34,066 --> 00:01:36,033
What his lover likes or dislikes?

20
00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:38,500
Are you crazy?

21
00:01:38,666 --> 00:01:40,266
When did I become your boyfriend?

22
00:01:41,933 --> 00:01:42,933
Just now.

23
00:01:45,033 --> 00:01:46,033
At this moment.

24
00:01:47,233 --> 00:01:48,400
And right now.

25
00:01:52,333 --> 00:01:53,333
Be my boyfriend.

26
00:01:54,333 --> 00:01:55,533
I'll take care of you.
